  "description": "This mod will add a tool that allow you to steal other player!",
  "body": "<h6><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ZJsZL5.png\" alt=\"Mod Banner\" width=\"1000\" height=\"270\"><strong><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/FUV3ZXctsUJ2UNi-ZCAXSYuQf5ErdIAtP-R6IL6f9t2BizQtZCxBXNWf-0I8D5viJayM_5ibumt9CFTkZpdgWYiHqFZ5sRLUmSk97TaxJxNz0VZfHOtXwzbrg8OIF7BMPBLBI811\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"></strong></h6>\n<h5><strong>What is Theft Mod?</strong></h5>\n<h6>Steal other players by crouching behind and using the Thief's Glove, steal as fast as possible before he sees you. Fully customizable mod.</h6>\n<h6><strong><br><br><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/OqfnOzj1MzvnDglYzoKysquKfmXbRW_HmzmqgWAZ5PBjZ_ttKjUioNlSmRADQysVdO4FxI8GoVHvcRpsODpej-Fhn1ePe4S10U9F7y6aDOAbqclCoHhEbeKFlIYiQRusMis-1M30\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"></strong></h6>\n<h5><strong>O que &eacute; Theft Mod? (Mod de Roubo)</strong></h5>\n<h6>Roube outros jogadores, chegue em suas costas, agache e use a Luva Do Ladr&atilde;o, roube o mais r&aacute;pido poss&iacute;vel, antes que ele veja. Mod totalmente personaliz&aacute;vel.<br><br></h6>\n<h5><strong>Some images:</strong></h5>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Stealing</em></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/C67nTgo.gif\" alt=\"stealing\" width=\"832\" height=\"468\"></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Victim's inventory</em></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/N29CnkA.png\" alt=\" Victim Inventory\" width=\"504\" height=\"366\"></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><em>Mod made by: Rokzin and Lucasmellof</em></strong></p>",
